            </h2>
            <p class="BodyText" style="margin-top:12.1pt">
                <span style="font-family:Arial">I/We </span><span
                    style="font-family:Arial; background-color:#ffff00"
                >{{fullName}}</span><span style="font-family:Arial">
                    have read and understood the terms and conditions of the
                    Research Analyst Services provided by Indo Thai Securities
                    Limited, including the fee structure and the mechanism for
                    charging and payment of fees. Based on my/our written
                    request to the Research Analyst, an opportunity was provided
                    by the Research Analyst to ask questions and interact with
                    the person(s) associated with the research services.</span>
            </p>
            <p class="BodyText" style="margin-top:12.1pt">
                <span style="font-family:Arial">&#xa0;</span>
            </p>
