            <h1
                style="margin-top:10.95pt; margin-left:18pt; text-indent:0pt; font-size:11pt"
            >
                <span style="font-weight:normal">The relationship between the
                    Client and the Research Analyst shall at all times be on a
                    principal-to-principal basis, and the Client acknowledges
                    that it has no authority to bind, represent, act for, or
                    incur any obligation on behalf of the Research Analyst.</span>
            </h1>
            <h1
                style="margin-top:10.95pt; margin-left:18pt; text-indent:0pt; font-size:11pt"
            >
                <span style="font-weight:normal">The services to be provided by
                    the Research Analyst shall include research, analysis,
                    preparation and dissemination of research reports, research
                    recommendations, model research strategies, and related
                    research content, all derived from publicly available
                    information and based on reasonable research methodologies.</span>
            </h1>
            <h1
                style="margin-top:10.95pt; margin-left:18pt; text-indent:0pt; font-size:11pt"
            >
                <span style="font-weight:normal">The Research Analyst does not
                    undertake or provide risk profiling, suitability assessment,
                    personalised investment advice, portfolio construction,
                    portfolio review, or any function that falls under the
                    purview of the SEBI Investment Adviser framework.</span>
            </h1>
            <h1
                style="margin-top:10.95pt; margin-left:18pt; text-indent:0pt; font-size:11pt"
            >
                <span style="font-weight:normal">The Research Analyst shall
                    provide research services during the term of this Agreement
                    in relation to securities, sectors, indices and investment
                    themes permitted under the SEBI Research Analyst
                    Regulations. All research opinions, views and
                    recommendations issued are non-binding, non-discretionary
                    and non-personalised, and the Client acknowledges that all
                    investment decisions taken on the basis of such research
                    shall be solely at the Client’s discretion and risk.</span>
            </h1>
            <h1
                style="margin-top:10.95pt; margin-left:18pt; text-indent:0pt; font-size:11pt"
            >
                <span style="font-weight:normal">Indo Thai Securities Limited
                    shall at all times act with integrity, objectivity,
                    independence and fairness, and in full compliance with the
                    Code of Conduct prescribed under the SEBI (Research
                    Analysts) Regulations, 2014.</span>
            </h1>
            <h1
                style="margin-top:10.95pt; margin-left:18pt; text-indent:0pt; font-size:11pt"
            >
                <span style="font-weight:normal">For avoidance of doubt, the
                    Research Analyst shall not act in a fiduciary capacity and
                    shall not provide portfolio management, execution or
                    order-placement services, shall not handle client funds or
                    securities, and shall not provide back-office or operational
                    support in relation to the Client’s investments</span>
            </h1>
            <p class="ListParagraph">
                <span style="font-family:Arial">&#xa0;</span>
            </p>
            <p class="ListParagraph">
                <span style="font-family:Arial">&#xa0;</span>
            </p>
            <ol start="4" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt">
                <li
                    class="ListParagraph"
                    style="margin-left:18pt; text-indent:3.3pt; font-family:Arial; font-weight:bold; list-style-position:inside"
                >
                    <span
                        style="width:0.53pt; font:7pt 'Times New Roman'; display:inline-block"
                    > </span>Duties and Functions of the Research Analyst (Short
                    &amp; Compliant)
                </li>
            </ol>
            <ol class="awlist1" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt">
                <li
                    class="ListParagraph"
                    style="margin-left:39.3pt; text-indent:-18pt; font-family:Arial; font-weight:bold"
                >
                    <span
                        style="width:4.56pt; font:7pt 'Times New Roman'; display:inline-block"
                    >&#xa0;&#xa0; </span>Compliance
                </li>
            </ol>
            <p class="ListParagraph" style="margin-left:39.3pt">
                <span style="font-family:Arial">The Research Analyst shall
                    perform its obligations strictly in accordance with the SEBI
                    (Research Analysts) Regulations, 2014, including all
                    amendments, circulars, and guidelines issued by SEBI or any
                    other competent authority. The Research Analyst confirms
                    that it meets all eligibility, certification and
                    fit-and-proper criteria and has no disciplinary restrictions
                    preventing it from acting as a SEBI-registered Research
                    Analyst.</span>
            </p>
            <ol start="2" class="awlist2" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt">
                <li
                    class="ListParagraph"
                    style="margin-top:0.85pt; margin-right:6.4pt; margin-left:39.3pt; text-indent:-18pt; font-family:Arial; font-weight:bold"
                >
                    <span
                        style="width:3.95pt; font:7pt 'Times New Roman'; display:inline-block"
                    >&#xa0;&#xa0; </span>Research Activity
                </li>
            </ol>
            <p
                class="ListParagraph"
                style="margin-top:0.85pt; margin-right:6.4pt; margin-left:39.3pt"
            >
                <span style="font-family:Arial">The Research Analyst shall
                    prepare and disseminate research reports, recommendations,
                    market analyses and related research material based solely
                    on publicly available information and reasonable research
                    processes. All research views are independent, objective and
                    non-personalised, and the Client acknowledges that acting
                    upon such research is entirely at the Client’s own
                    discretion.</span>
            </p>
            <ol start="3" class="awlist3" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt">
                <li
                    class="ListParagraph"
                    style="margin-top:0.85pt; margin-right:6.4pt; margin-left:39.3pt; text-indent:-18pt; font-family:Arial; font-weight:bold"
                >
                    <span
                        style="width:4.56pt; font:7pt 'Times New Roman'; display:inline-block"
                    >&#xa0;&#xa0; </span>Record-Keeping
                </li>
            </ol>
            <p
                class="ListParagraph"
                style="margin-top:0.85pt; margin-right:6.4pt; margin-left:39.3pt"
            >
                <span style="font-family:Arial">The Research Analyst shall
                    maintain all records required under the SEBI Research
                    Analyst Regulations, including research reports issued,
                    underlying data and rationale, disclosures made, and
                    relevant communications. The Research Analyst is not
                    required to maintain KYC, suitability, or risk-profiling
                    records because these fall under the Investment Adviser
                    framework.</span>
            </p>
            <ol start="4" class="awlist4" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt">
                <li
                    class="ListParagraph"
                    style="margin-top:0.85pt; margin-right:6.4pt; margin-left:39.3pt; text-indent:-18pt; font-family:Arial; font-weight:bold"
                >
                    <span
                        style="width:3.95pt; font:7pt 'Times New Roman'; display:inline-block"
                    >&#xa0;&#xa0; </span>Regulatory Cooperation
                </li>
            </ol>
            <p
                class="ListParagraph"
                style="margin-top:0.85pt; margin-right:6.4pt; margin-left:39.3pt"
            >
                <span style="font-family:Arial">The Research Analyst shall
                    cooperate with SEBI or any regulatory authority in any
                    inspection, audit or supervisory review and shall comply
                    with all regulatory obligations applicable to Research
                    Analysts.</span>
            </p>
            <ol start="5" class="awlist5" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt">
                <li
                    class="ListParagraph"
                    style="margin-top:0.85pt; margin-right:6.4pt; margin-left:39.3pt; text-indent:-18pt; font-family:Arial; font-weight:bold"
                >
                    <span
                        style="width:4.56pt; font:7pt 'Times New Roman'; display:inline-block"
                    >&#xa0;&#xa0; </span>Code of Conduct
                </li>
            </ol>
            <p
                class="ListParagraph"
                style="margin-top:0.85pt; margin-right:6.4pt; margin-left:39.3pt"
            >
                <span style="font-family:Arial">Indo Thai Securities Limited
                    undertakes to follow the Code of Conduct prescribed in the
                    Third Schedule of the SEBI (Research Analysts) Regulations,
                    including principles of integrity, independence, fairness,
                    conflict-management and proper disclosure.</span>
            </p>
            <ol start="6" class="awlist6" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt">
                <li
                    class="ListParagraph"
                    style="margin-top:0.85pt; margin-right:6.4pt; margin-left:39.3pt; text-indent:-18pt; font-family:Arial; font-weight:bold"
                >
                    <span
                        style="width:7.01pt; font:7pt 'Times New Roman'; display:inline-block"
                    >&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; </span>No Legal/Tax Advice
                </li>
            </ol>
            <p
