            </h2>
            <p
                class="BodyText"
                style="margin-top:3.95pt; margin-right:0pt; margin-left:0pt; text-align:left"
            >
                <strong><span style="font-family:Arial; ">&#xa0;</span></strong>
            </p>
            <p
                style="margin-right:163.95pt; margin-left:161.25pt; text-align:center"
            >
                <strong><span style="font-family:Arial; ">Research Analyst
                        Services</span></strong>
            </p>
            <p style="margin-right:6.4pt; margin-left:16.4pt">
                <strong><span style="font-family:Arial; ">&#xa0;</span></strong>
            </p>
            <p style="margin-right:6.4pt">
                <span style="font-family:Arial">The Research Analyst (“RA”)
                    shall provide the following services exclusively through
                    online modes, strictly in accordance with the SEBI (Research
                    Analysts) Regulations, 2014 and the SEBI RA Master Circular:</span>
            </p>
            <p
                class="ListParagraph"
                style="margin-right:6.4pt; margin-left:29.35pt"
            >
                <span style="font-family:Arial">&#xa0;</span>
            </p>
            <ol style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt">
                <li
                    class="ListParagraph"
                    style="margin-right:6.4pt; margin-left:29.35pt"
                >
                    <span style="font-family:Arial">Preparation and
                        dissemination of research reports relating to listed
                        securities, issuers, sectors, industries, market
                        movements, and macro-economic developments, based
                        entirely on publicly available information and
                        reasonable research methodologies.</span>
                </li>
                <li
                    class="ListParagraph"
                    style="margin-right:6.4pt; margin-left:29.35pt"
                >
                    <span style="font-family:Arial">Provision of
                        non-personalized investment recommendations or general
                        views on securities and investment strategies, without
                        taking into account any specific client’s financial
                        situation, risk profile, or investment objectives,
                        unless expressly permitted under SEBI regulations.</span>
                </li>
                <li
                    class="ListParagraph"
                    style="margin-right:6.4pt; margin-left:29.35pt"
                >
                    <span style="font-family:Arial">Issuance of revisions,
                        updates and follow-up research on previously published
                        opinions, including changes in views, ratings, or
                        conclusions whenever material developments occur.</span>
                </li>
                <li
                    class="ListParagraph"
                    style="margin-right:6.4pt; margin-left:29.35pt"
                >
                    <span style="font-family:Arial">Sharing of market
                        intelligence and data-driven insights relating to
                        corporate announcements, earnings results, economic
                        indicators, regulatory updates, and sector-related
                        developments that may impact covered securities.</span>
                </li>
                <li
                    class="ListParagraph"
                    style="margin-right:6.4pt; margin-left:29.35pt"
                >
                    <span style="font-family:Arial">Providing educational
                        research content, including explanatory notes on
                        valuation approaches, sector overviews, methodology
                        summaries, and materials intended to help clients
                        understand market behaviour and the analytical basis of
                        the RA’s research.</span>
                </li>
                <li
                    class="ListParagraph"
                    style="margin-right:6.4pt; margin-left:29.35pt"
                >
                    <span style="font-family:Arial">Maintaining transparency of
                        research methodology and regulatory disclosures,
                        including mandatory disclosures of conflicts of
                        interest, ownership or beneficial interest in covered
                        securities, compensation arrangements, relationships or
                        affiliations, and all relevant risk factors and
                        disclaimers.</span>
                </li>
                <li
                    class="ListParagraph"
                    style="margin-right:6.4pt; margin-left:29.35pt"
                >
                    <span style="font-family:Arial">Responding to reasonable
                        client queries relating to the RA’s research content,
                        analytical rationale, data interpretation, or sector
                        outlook, without offering execution assistance,
                        portfolio management, or personalized investment advice.</span>
                </li>
                <li
                    class="ListParagraph"
                    style="margin-right:6.4pt; margin-left:29.35pt"
                >
                    <span style="font-family:Arial">Maintaining all required
                        records such as research drafts, data sources,
                        assumptions, communications related to research, and
                        published reports for the duration prescribed under SEBI
                        regulations.</span>
                </li>
            </ol>
            <p
                class="ListParagraph"
                style="margin-right:6.4pt; margin-left:29.35pt"
            >
                <span style="font-family:Arial">&#xa0;</span>
            </p>
            <p style="margin-right:6.4pt">
                <span style="font-family:Arial">For clarity, the RA shall not
                    undertake implementation of recommendations, execution of
                    trades, supervision or management of client portfolios,
                    personalised financial advice, financial planning, or any
                    activity outside the scope permitted to Research Analysts.
                    All activities shall strictly remain within the domain of
                    research and analysis as defined under the SEBI (Research
                    Analysts) Regulations, 2014..</span>
            </p>
